<org.eclipse.epf.uma:ContentDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmlns:rmc="http://www.ibm.com/rmc" rmc:version="7.5.1" xmi:id="-fW3FrAxrteP133E2B_Ib-Q" name="reduce_infrastructure_costs,_yj7DMMx-Ed6AlLazTePGRg" guid="-fW3FrAxrteP133E2B_Ib-Q" changeDate="2009-12-16T10:23:35.359-0800" version="7.5.0">
  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Description&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Effectively drive down infrastructure costs associated with legacy applications. Infrastructure costs include:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        maintenance costs for software and hardware&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Software licenses&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Servers&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Power and facilities&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Symptoms&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Symptoms that indicate the need to reduce infrastructure costs include:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Multiple&amp;nbsp;infrastructures to support multiple platforms (server sprawl).&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Infrastructure is costly and difficult to maintain.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Duplication of data across servers.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Solutions&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following solutions help to reduce infrastructure costs:&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    High Impact:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_transformation_6C08D1F9.html&quot; guid=&quot;_uyUeYLbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application Transformation&lt;/a> - Transform applications using modern architectures&#xD;
        and technologies while leveraging existing investments.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/rearchitect_for_reuse_503CC74C.html&quot; guid=&quot;_Gc7bsMyEEd6AlLazTePGRg&quot;>Re-Architect for Reuse&lt;/a> - Re-architect existing solutions to improve reusability&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_re-platforming_FDA9E88B.html&quot; guid=&quot;_yVtsoLbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application Re-Platforming&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;- Move applications to more modern platforms&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/improve_developer_effectiveness_1089DC4C.html&quot; guid=&quot;_0MmLMLbHEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Improve Developer Effectiveness&lt;/a> - Reduce manual work by developers by&#xD;
        leveraging existing patterns and automated tools to transform model to model or model to code.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Medium Impact:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/determine_app_modernization_strategy_432C5B90.html&quot; guid=&quot;_lZz24LbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Determine Application Modernization Strategy&lt;/a> -&amp;nbsp;Create a roadmap to&#xD;
        modernize applications&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/optimizing_server_utilization_5D37BA9E.html&quot; guid=&quot;_xDOpYOaREd6w5Z3dNqpXmw&quot;>Optimizing Server Utilization&lt;/a> - Optimize server workloads to maximize the value&#xD;
        returned by the server infrastructure to the business.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/improve_build_process_9E509595.html&quot; guid=&quot;_eOf00LRZEd6qwtTa3nKvcw&quot;>Improve Build Processes&lt;/a> - Increase Build and Test automation to reduce manual&#xD;
        and insufficient build and test procedures.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/improve_test_effectiveness_F97F58E1.html&quot; guid=&quot;_xwg3AMyDEd6AlLazTePGRg&quot;>Improve Test Effectiveness&lt;/a> - Improve the effectiveness of testing activities by&#xD;
        improving test procedures and increasing the percentage of automated tests.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Low Impact:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_ui_modernization_88264BD3.html&quot; guid=&quot;_qcHTILbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application UI Modernization&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;- Extend the value of existing solutions in a&#xD;
        cost effective manner by modernizing their user interfaces&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
